About

Welcome to Buds and Petals! Founded in 2024 by Molly Branch, Buds and Petals grows and nurtures a diverse collection of plants, from vibrant flowers to lush houseplants and everything in between.

At Buds and Petals, we believe that everyone can experience the joy of gardening, no matter their skill level. Our knowledgeable team is here to offer personalized advice, ensuring you find the perfect plants for your home or garden. We take pride in sourcing our plants sustainably and supporting local growers, so you can feel good about your choices.

Join us for workshops, seasonal events, and a community of fellow plant lovers. Whether you’re a seasoned gardener or just starting out, we’re here to inspire and help you cultivate your green thumb.

Thank you for choosing Buds and Petals—where your gardening journey begins!

Hear from the Founder!

Molly Branch

Born in Cincinnati, Ohio, Molly Branch had a love for plants from a small age. As a child, she would often help her parents plant their backyard garden. As she got older, she grew her own collection of potted plants.

After graduating from college with a bachelor's in business, Molly made the decision to open up her own plant nursery, providing the communities she grew up in with a beautiful array of plants.
